{"title":"the Q&A of Bear","date":"2022-11-21T14:21:04.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Nov 21, 2022","L":"11/21/2022","MM-DD":"11-21"},"link":"project/swift-bearqna","comments":true,"tags":["swift"],"categories":["project"],"updated":"2022-11-21T14:27:02.826Z","content":"<blockquote>\n<p>使用 shuffle 製作隨機出題小遊戲</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h4 id=\"app內容\">APP內容<a title=\"#app內容\" href=\"#app內容\"></a></h4>\n<ul>\n<li>題目為隨機出題</li>\n<li>答案選項順序隨機</li>\n<li>Play Again 重新挑戰遊戲</li>\n<li>使用 shuffle() 打亂順序</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"app-畫面\">APP 畫面<a title=\"#app-畫面\" href=\"#app-畫面\"></a></h4>\n<div >\n<div>\n<img src='https://miro.medium.com/max/640/1*TXfCemNWV97KxcmPyBafWA.png' width='180'/>\n<img src='https://miro.medium.com/max/640/1*IZziK6ua4MfrWGBmhOT4pA.png' width='180'/>\n<img src='https://miro.medium.com/max/640/1*L8ldjWVOV1DSAuKj2FFXrA.png' width='180'/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<h4 id=\"操作畫面\">操作畫面<a title=\"#操作畫面\" href=\"#操作畫面\"></a></h4>\n<div style='text-align: center' >\n<img src='https://miro.medium.com/max/628/1*M-W2-eoLsKoi76CD91rJfg.gif' width='250'/>\n</div >\n<h4 id=\"程式碼片段\">程式碼片段<a title=\"#程式碼片段\" href=\"#程式碼片段\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight swift\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">qnas.shuffle() <span class=\"comment\">// random question</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">qnas[number].choice.shuffle() <span class=\"comment\">// random choice</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"github專案連結\">Github專案連結<a title=\"#github專案連結\" href=\"#github專案連結\"></a></h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/Junghc/BearQna\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/Junghc/BearQna</a></p>\n<hr>","next":{"title":"E book - Winnie the pooh","link":"project/swift-ebook"},"plink":"https://junghc.github.io/project/swift-bearqna/","reading_time":"117 words in 1 min"}